headline.print_headline: Forces From Libyan City of Misrata Say They Seized Tripoli Airport
headline.main: Forces From Libyan City of Misrata Say They Seized Tripoli Airport

lead_paragraph: Forces from the Libyan city of Misrata on Saturday seized Tripoli's main airport after more than a month of fighting with a rival group, a Misrata spokesman said.
